---

<section class="relative pb-20 bg-background-dark">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-800"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-surface-dark/50 p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-start border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-gray-800"
      >
        <div class="opacity-50 flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              height="32px"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              width="32px"
              fill="#e3e3e3"
              ><path d="M0 0h24v24H0V0z" fill="none"></path><path
                d="M12.5 6.9c1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-.39.08-.75.21-1.1.36l1.51 1.51c.32-.08.69-.13 1.09-.13zM5.47 3.92L4.06 5.33 7.5 8.77c0 2.08 1.56 3.22 3.91 3.91l3.51 3.51c-.34.49-1.05.91-2.42.91-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c.96-.18 1.83-.55 2.46-1.12l2.22 2.22 1.41-1.41L5.47 3.92z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-400">Traditional Model</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 pl-12 mb-6">
            How dubbing services usually work
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-500">
          <p class="flex text-xl items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            High Upfront Costs (CapEx)
          </p>
          <p class="flex text-xl items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            Monthly Retainers (OpEx)
          </p>
          <p class="flex text-xl items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            Financial Risk on Creator
          </p>
          <p class="flex text-xl items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            Misaligned Incentives
          </p>
          <p class="flex text-xl items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            Fixed Costs Regardless of Results
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-dark to-primary/10 p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>

        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 relative z-10"
        >
          Not OpEx. Not CapEx.
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert relative z-10">
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            You don't pay us. You don't hire us. We <span
              class="text-white font-semibold"
            >
              invest in your channel
            </span> by dubbing your content into new languages, building new audiences,
            and splitting the revenue
            <span class="text-primary font-semibold">50/50</span>.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
            When your dubbed content grows, we both win. That's not a fee
            structure â€” it's a <span class="text-white font-semibold"
              >partnership built on shared success</span
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4 text-primary font-medium text-xl"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            height="32px"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            width="32px"
            fill="#22c55e"
            ><path d="M0 0h24v24H0V0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6h-6z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          <span>Growth Driven</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
